{"tid":1365727,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正聲明：「仁義禮智」絕不適用於警犬、建制狗同現任高官","createTime":"2019-07-25T17:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T17:59:27.000Z","uid":2617,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5c5e93b812c7fae093119d137fb66c145b6554","tid":1365727,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:27:40.000Z","msg":"仁──即無私的普遍的惻隱不忍之心。孝悌為仁之本。<br />\n義──本於人格尊嚴之自覺，而以公平正直之心，對人接物皆為義。人之義極於犧牲生命以見氣節，<br />\n禮──見於自己謙讓與對他人之尊重。人之禮，極於尊敬一切人倫世界人文世界中之人。<br />\n智──見於明辨是與非。人之智極於使人我皆能不違真理，同得改過遷善。<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母閪<br />\n係呢班政府建制同黑警呢隊物種上面 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(必須重申: 係物種唔係人)</span></span><br />\n你幾撚時睇到呢四樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊記不割蓆原則<br />\n所以我決定<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論任何人對呢班物種(及其相關物種與工作環境)<br />\n作出任何攻擊行為<br />\n我會對佢地予以最崇高既敬意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a6c0375fa8a7c1c792266ddc3d599334ca32c739","tid":1365727,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f688c1da3bd41f2668f72749986516cdfe748d","tid":1365727,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5079079c374c0c1d1d1381b067f27436f8c903","tid":1365727,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:36:25.000Z","msg":"希望大家從呢班物種身上學下做人"},{"pid":"c3488ffa21c81e1048d5972a46e12ee32e4b38ff","tid":1365727,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3831f7d1cfcfb6e28d983f36829be907f5ac9e","tid":1365727,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,